author: Alisha Ebrahimji, CNN
title: The ICU nurse who silently stood in protest at a rally to reopen Arizona
description: On her day off from working at a Covid-19 unit in an Arizona hospital, ICU nurse Lauren Leander threw on clean scrubs and headed to an anti-lockdown protest at the state Capitol. She was determined to be a voice for her patients through silence.
